{"arkId":"cl010120546","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010120546","modified ":"2026-01-14","title":"statue","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"statue (fragment)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Dynastique archa\u00efque IIIB (Vers 2500-2400 av. J. - C.) (-2500 - -2340)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [AO] Salle 234 - Mari. Le nord de la M\u00e9sopotamie \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9poque Dynastique Archa\u00efque (2600 \u2013 2300 av. J.-C.), Vitrine 3 D\u00e9p\u00f4ts votifs du temple d\u2019Ishtar","room":"Salle 234, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-2500,"endYear":-2340,"imprecision":"","text":"Dynastique archa\u00efque IIIB","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 18212","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"M. 541","type":"N\u00b0 de fouille"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"femme (polos)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : \u00e9br\u00e9ch\u00e9\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : T\u00eate d\u0027une statue de femme coiff\u00e9e du polos. Les sourcils et les yeux \u00e9taient incrust\u00e9s. La pupille des yeux a disparu, il ne reste que le bitume et la coquille. La chevelure incis\u00e9e encadre le visage ; cavit\u00e9 au niveau des oreilles pour retenir des parures. Le nez et le menton sont \u00e9br\u00e9ch\u00e9s.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14,8","displayDimension":"14,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"12,6","displayDimension":"12,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"8,8","displayDi